{"type": "article", "id": 15631, "title": "这些毛衣有点酷，它把音乐、设计和针织搞在了一起", "description": "有了摇滚乐队和艺术家的参与，这个希望或许也不是梦。", "date": "2015-09-29T08:35:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2499, "name": "毛衣"}, {"id": 16718, "name": "摇滚乐队"}, {"id": 7968, "name": "Coolhunting"}, {"id": 16719, "name": "WAH-WAH"}, {"id": 16720, "name": "Kaylene Milner"}], "category": 19, "column": 24, "author": 18, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 146, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061600297WEYid2sBl3RKcwq.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong><a href=\"http://www.coolhunting.com/style/wah-wah-knitwear-australia\" target=\"_blank\"><em>本文</em></a><em>由 Coolhunting 授权《好奇心日报》发表，即使我们同意了也不能转载。</em></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>穿</span><span>“</span><span>难看的毛衣</span><span>”</span><span>的季节</span><span>到来了</span><span>，满眼都是大麻主题和</span><span> </span><span>Tumblr</span><span> </span><span>式的设计，但有个 </span><span><a href=\"http://www.wahwahaustralia.com/\"><span>WAH-WAH Australia</span></a></span><span> </span><span>品牌不走寻常路（</span><span>尽管也很欢乐花哨）。</span><span>由 Kaylene Milner 牵头的</span><span> </span><span>WAH-WAH 品牌与当地乐队合作</span><span>，</span><span>创造</span><span>出了</span><span>一种非常规</span><span>、有意思的</span><span>毛衣。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>你可以把它看做是演唱会的周边</span><span>产品</span><span>，</span><span>只</span><span>不过是针织衫形式的。设计</span><span>的</span><span>主题一点也不含蓄——</span><span>有一件</span><span>是</span><span>用</span><span>魔幻图案向</span><span> </span><span>Donna Chang</span><span> </span><span>致敬</span><span>的</span><span>，这也是该品牌与澳洲朋克</span><span> </span><span>The Hard-Ons</span><span> 、</span><span>迷幻七人</span><span>组 </span><span>King Gizzard &amp; the Lizard Wizard</span><span> </span><span>等</span><span>乐队</span><span>合作的首批产品。我们与这家公司的创始人、设计师</span><span>，</span><span>几乎一人</span><span>包揽产品线</span><span>的 Milner 谈了</span><span>谈让人</span><span>满意的怪胎</span><span>、</span><span>令人费解的设计</span><span>、</span><span>她的创业</span><span>历程，以及</span><span>如何将</span><span>全部热情都倾入</span><span>一门生意中。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160028KMyLi4lo6UjBdhWQ.jpg\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.74537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>“</span><span>WAH-WAH 是我一个人运营的，但设计方面与很多我欣赏的乐队、艺术家合作，</span><span>”</span><span>Milner 说。</span><span>“</span><span>这个想法</span><span>是</span><span>我十年前</span><span>在</span><span>脑子里种下的种子，</span><span>我</span><span>想</span><span>要</span><span>设计与乐队相关的</span><span>毛衣</span><span>——其实那会儿我还在上高中。我在读 Michael Azerrad 的书《我们的乐队可能成为你的生活：美国独立地下音乐记录》（Our Band Could Be Your Life: Scenes from the American Indie Underground），看到了一张照片，J Mascis 穿着一件她妈妈为</span><span>他</span><span>织的</span><span> </span><span>Deep Wound</span><span> </span><span>的毛衣。我</span><span>还</span><span>记得</span><span>，</span><span>那时候</span><span>我</span><span>作为一个青少年，觉得这简直太酷了！</span><span>”</span><span>今年早些时候，Milner</span><span> 感觉</span><span>自己</span><span>已经有</span><span>经验和技能来设计自己的毛衣了，于是开始做一个同名的时装品牌，</span><span>后来</span><span>并不尽如人意，因为</span><span>她</span><span>并不想做成</span><span>那种</span><span>按季发布的商业化时装系列，于是 Milner 做</span><span>出</span><span>了 WAH-WAH。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160029tNY7uKDGL1ycH4QC.jpg\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.74722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>第一个系列只有</span><span> </span><span>5 件针织衫（每件含</span><span> </span><span>80% 羊毛），Milner 与她自己喜欢的艺术家和乐队合作。</span><span>“</span><span>The Hard-Ons 乐队的 Ray Ahn 是我第一个交流这个想法的人。问他的时候我真挺紧张的，但幸运的是，他喜欢</span><span>我的</span><span>想法。我一直很钦佩他的</span><span>专辑和</span><span>海报作品，</span><span>能</span><span>和一个我喜欢的本地乐队合作</span><span>，</span><span>作为开端</span><span>也很</span><span>合适，而且他有很强的视觉</span><span>艺术背景</span><span>。WAH-WAH 是个我</span><span>非常个人化</span><span>的项目。这是</span><span>一</span><span>个我自己想出来</span><span>的</span><span>方式，能把我爱的音乐、设计和针织衫结合</span><span>在一起</span><span>，我还能用打破常规的方式来实现</span><span>它</span><span>，</span><span>”</span><span>她说。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160029EYAIrVBPRovUtJi1.jpg\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.74166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>目前，Miltebiner </span><span>正</span><span>与悉尼</span><span>的</span><span>一家</span><span>生产商</span><span>合作，她相信对方能把</span><span>她</span><span>复杂的设计</span><span>忠实</span><span>展现出来。</span><span>“</span><span>我与我的制造商密切合作，</span><span>让</span><span>我们的设计能通过机器编织实现，</span><span>”</span><span>她说。</span><span>“</span><span>将来</span><span>，我</span><span>可能还会做些特别</span><span>的</span><span>手工针织</span><span>单品</span><span>，</span><span>大概可以</span><span>作为收藏品吧？</span><span>”</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>澳洲 WAH-WAH 可以</span><span><a href=\"http://www.wahwahaustralia.bigcartel.com/\"><span>在线购买</span></a></span><span>，针织衫售价 240 澳元。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>图片来源 WAH-WAH      </span><span>翻译 Alicia Lee</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}